'''Azin or Andzin Rinpoche''' is an incarnate lama ([[tulku]]) in the [[Karma Kagyu]] school of [[Tibetan Buddhism]] associated with Palnge Monastery in [[Gegyal]]. Their [[reincarnation]]s have been known for strict retreat practices and diligence in mastering the [[sutra]]s. They have also been closely associated with [[Sherap Monastery]] and [[Tai Situpa]] as many of the reincarnations received their education there.

The current incarnation, Karma Thubten Trinlay Gyurme, was born on 22 March 1984.

